# ── .NET / calibration bridge build output ────────────────────────────────
# The bridge project (bridge/SimLinkupCalibrationBridge.sln) builds via
# MSBuild and emits per-project bin/ and obj/ directories. The Release-
# x86 build is what gets bundled into the installer via electron-builder's
# extraResources, but it's produced at build time on the GitHub Actions
# runner — not committed.
bin/
obj/
*.user
*.suo
.vs/
packages/
TestResults/
*.pdb
